# Title: SugusGuard DOH filter
# Description: SugusGuard's Bad-DNS filterlist for AdGuard Home / AdGuard Pro App
# DoH, DoT Servers that seems to be forced in some Software or simply unwanted
# List-URL: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SugusGuard/Blocklists/main/SugusGuardDOH
# Date: 2022-05-31
#
##  CLOUDFLARE
#
||cloudflare-dns.com^$dnsrewrite=REFUSED,important
||one.one.one.one^$dnsrewrite=REFUSED,important
||ns.cloudflare.com^$dnsrewrite=REFUSED,important
||dns.cloudflare.com^$dnsrewrite=REFUSED,important
